        [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]
        [0, 1, 2, 3, 5]
        [0, 1, 2, 4, 5]
        [0, 1, 2, 4, 6]
        [0, 1, 3, 4, 5]

    However, we do not allow infinitely many lists of the same length::

        sage: IntegerLists(4, min_part=-infinity, length=3, min_slope=1).list()
        Traceback (most recent call last):
        ...
